## Privacy Considerations

**Exclude from recaps:**
- Sensitive performance feedback (unless explicitly shared in 1:1)
- Salary/compensation discussions
- Confidential org information
- Personal struggles (unless appropriate to acknowledge)

**Always include:**
- Action items (clear accountability)
- Key decisions made
- Timeline commitments
